-Validating an existing esxi host icsi configuration. 
-Navigate to Storage Adapters and click okay
-Storage Adapters is created.
-Select iscsi and click ok
-Name icsi and Click on OK
-On network port binding and click on add then click ok
-Write ip address of host.
-Go to Dynamic Discovery. and click ok
-Select VMkernel Network Adapter and click next
-Configuring port properties for VM kernel and click next 
-click on Finish
-now virtual network is added. 
